-a [process files of all users]
-A [print today and the following num days]
-b [enforce special KOI8 date calculation mode]
-B [print today and the previous num days]
-f [use file as the default calendar]
-l [print today and the following num days]
-w [print today and the following num days only if today is Friday]
-t [act as though today is the date specified]
